content.rendered:
Directed By Ravi Jadhav

Written By Priyadarshan Jadhav

Stars Priya Bapat (Flashback Scenes as Prajakta). Sameer Chowgule (College Principal). Hruta Durgule (Palvi Dinkar Patil). Bhau Kadam (Shantaram Parab). Vaibhav Mangale (Madhav Lele). Sanjay Narvekar (Dinkar Patil). Prathamesh Parab (Dagdu Shantaram Parab (DSP)). Manmeet Pem (Balbharti). Anvita Phaltankar (Chanda (Chandramukhi)). Onkar Raut (Kombdya). Sandy (Pakya). Prashant Tapasvi (College Peon). Aarti Wadagbalkar (Manda). Jayesh Chandrakant Chavan (Malaria (uncredited)). Ketaki Mategaonkar (Flashback Scenes as Prajakta).

Language Marathi

Producer Meghana Jadhav

Production Zee Studios. Athaansh Communications
